# Release notes - OpenCart - Release 1 - Place an order

### Bug

[OP-93](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-93) \[Mandatory field\] No value in "Qty" field returns a validation message

[OP-94](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-94) \[Invalid data\] Product added to cart when a decimal number is entered for quantity

[OP-95](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-95) \[Invalid data\] Validation message of a product added to cart, when a decimal number is entered for quantity

[OP-97](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-97) \[Invalid data\] Validation message when letters are entered for quantity

[OP-98](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-98) \[Invalid data\] Validation message when special characters are entered for quantity

[OP-99](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-99) \[Invalid data\] The product is added to cart even when the delivery date is in the past

[OP-100](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-100) \[Invalid data\] Validation message when "0" value is entered for quantity

[OP-101](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-101) \[UI\] The shopping cart black button has invisible text when mouse hover

[OP-102](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-102) \[Data\] "Address 1" field does not accept 128 characters, containing special characters

[OP-103](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-103) \[Data\] "City" field does not accept maximum 128 characters

[OP-104](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-104) \[Data\] "Password" field does not accept maximum 20 characters

[OP-105](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-105) \[Data\] For "Guest checkout" option, the "Continue" button does not save the account when all mandatory fields are completed

[OP-106](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-106) \[Data\] For "Guest checkout" option, the "Continue" button does not save the account when all fields are completed

[OP-107](https://op3ncar7.atlassian.net/browse/OP-107) \[Specifications\] The documentation is not clear and complete

